Message: Hello, Binay! I'm here to assist you.
Hi, Can I know something more about the transportation system.
There are buses running every 30 minutes around campus and to nearby areas. You can use the student bus pass to travel, Binay.
Yeah nice, can you tell me something more about the cafeteria, or maybe smething about coffee.
The coffee bar serves freshly brewed coffee, Binay. You should definitely try their specialty drinks!
